This is a library for implementing Ocaml jobs for the Disco map-reduce framework.

Prerequisites:
--------------

. ocaml 3.12.0, ocamlfind/findlib

. libzip-ocaml-dev (Debian/Ubuntu) / godi-zip (Godi) / camlzip (source)

. sonet
   $ git clone git://github.com/pmundkur/sonet.git
   $ cd sonet && make install

   To uninstall:
   $ cd sonet && make uninstall

Building:
---------

 $ make

Using:
------

. Write a module implementing the lib/task:TASK interface, and pass
  this module to Worker.start in your main program.  See
  tests/test_task.ml for an example.

. Use the bin/discojob.py program to submit your compiled executable
  to Disco.

Status:
-------

Currently under heavy development.
